t \in [0,\frac{\pi}{2}]
P_{n}(\operatorname{cotan}^2t)=\frac{\sin((2n+1)t}{(\sin t)^{2n+1}}
\operatorname{cotan}(x)=\frac{\cos x}{\sin x}
