n
P_n(x) = \sum_{l=0}^{n} \binom{2n+1}{2l+1} (-1)^l x^{n-l}
\frac{\sin((2n+1)t)}{\sin^{2n+1}t} = \sum_{l=0}^{n} \binom{2n+1}{2l+1} (-1)^l \Big(\frac{\cos^2t}{\sin^{2} t}\Big)^{n-l} = P_n(\cot^2 t), 
